mil.emp3.api.events

Class MapUserInteractionEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.emp3.api.events.Event<UserInteractionEventEnum,TargetType>
      • mil.emp3.api.events.UserInteractionEvent<IMap>
        • mil.emp3.api.events.MapUserInteractionEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEvent<UserInteractionEventEnum,IMap>

    public abstract class MapUserInteractionEvent
extends UserInteractionEvent<IMap>
    This event is generated when the user interacts with a specific map. To register for this event you must instantiate an object that implements the IMapInteractionEventListener interface and register for the event on an IMap.
